text: Le Castelet is a commune. It is found in the region Normandy in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2019 and consists of the former communes of Saint-Aignan-de-Cramesnil (the seat) and Garcelles-Secqueville.Arrêté préfectoral 24 September 2018, p. 129 == References == Category:2019 establishments in France Category:Communes in Calvados
title: Le Castelet
